om/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.io%2Farticle%2F161119&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5Clnb%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=a61ea1c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.io/article/161119</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T00:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T00:36:47.000Z","msg":"老闆嚟講<br />\n<br />\n佢真係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T00:59:04.000Z","msg":"cctvb 最好做最佛心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bd045a98c2a1e2b4ef77774f448f0630fb55c8","tid":2499355,"uid":45603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"747beffdc3888528b1314fa83494fa7f1f53dbcb","tid":2499355,"uid":51615,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"304c3c33bee2cf9407a94398c45452bf35fa50d7","tid":2499355,"uid":65790,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T00:02:03.000Z","msg":"又掂左<br />\n魔童即係魔童<br />\n<br />\n比起做電視大潛力好多<br />\n大把空間發展，香港Shopify<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟係一早plan定定689玩野後先決定呢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T00:26:41.000Z","msg":"好彩佢無撈電視，而家viu做得好好<br />\n維基做網購<br />\n楷仔做電視<br />\n全方位打殘無線電視"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:00:18.000Z","msg":"有佢就冇viu啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8187df27aee460f2297c982609aff279ef4b78","tid":2499355,"uid":3365